# DC file conventions

## Runtime

- `support.js` provides DCLogic / React bindings — do not break `<x-dc>` structure
- Interactive logic lives in `<script type="text/x-dc" data-dc-script>` class extending `DCLogic`
- Template bindings: `{{ variable }}`, `onClick="{{ handler }}"`, `<sc-if test="{{ flag }}">`

## Preserve data hooks

Do not rename without updating JS:
- `[data-rv]` scroll reveal, `[data-count]` counters, `[data-svc]` / `[data-svc-id]` services
- `[data-rail]` / `[data-rail-item]` section nav, `[data-chroma]` lab chromatogram
- `[data-anim]`, `[data-sec]`, `[data-nav]`, `[data-burger]`, `[data-proj]`, `[data-steps]`

## Master file

`NIC Ecolog - Главная v2.dc.html` is the homepage source of truth.
v1 (`NIC Ecolog - Главная.dc.html`) is legacy — do not sync back to v1.

## Assets

Relative paths: `./assets/`, `./support.js`, `./image-slot.js`
